{"title":"JVM 工具集","date":"2023-04-06T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年4月6日","L":"2023/04/06","MM-DD":"04-06"},"thumbnail":"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/642e3c67a682492fcc7861d2.png","link":"jvm-tools","tags":["JVM"],"categories":["JVM"],"updated":"2023-04-05T16:00:00.000Z","content":"<h3 id=\"jvisualvm(java-visualvm)\">jvisualvm(Java VisualVM)<a title=\"#jvisualvm(java-visualvm)\" href=\"#jvisualvm(java-visualvm)\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/642e3c67a682492fcc7861d2.png\" alt=\"Java VisualVM\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>随JDK一同发布的jvm诊断工具<br>\n但是没有GC可视化, 需要安装插件, 看下面步骤</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h6 id=\"visual-gc-离线插件安装\">Visual GC 离线插件安装<a title=\"#visual-gc-离线插件安装\" href=\"#visual-gc-离线插件安装\"></a></h6>\n<p>官网：<a href=\"https://visualvm.github.io/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://visualvm.github.io/index.html</a><br>\n点击：Plugins<br>\n点击：Plugins Centers<br>\n找到：Java VisualVM 对应JDK版本：<code>JDK 8 Update 131 - 341</code> &gt; <code>https://visualvm.github.io/uc/8u131/updates.xml.gz</code><br>\n找到：Tools 目录<br>\n点击： Visual GC 下载</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"memory-analyzer-(eclipse-mat)\">Memory Analyzer (Eclipse MAT)<a title=\"#memory-analyzer-(eclipse-mat)\" href=\"#memory-analyzer-(eclipse-mat)\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/6430e5360d2dde5777f3c0f6.png\" alt=\"Java VisualVM\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个快速且功能丰富的Java堆分析器, 它可以帮助您查找内存泄漏并减少内存消耗.<br>\n内存监控和分析<br>\n内存泄漏分析工具</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>官方网站: <a href=\"https://www.eclipse.org/mat/downloads.php\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eclipse.org/mat/downloads.php</a></p>\n<p>历史JDK版本可以点击:<code>Previous Releases</code> 下载符合自己JDK的版本</p>\n<p>官方介绍页面: <a href=\"https://wiki.eclipse.org/MemoryAnalyzer#About\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.eclipse.org/MemoryAnalyzer#About</a><br>\n官方教程页面: <a href=\"https://help.eclipse.org/latest/index.jsp?topic=/org.eclipse.mat.ui.help/gettingstarted/basictutorial.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://help.eclipse.org/latest/index.jsp?topic=/org.eclipse.mat.ui.help/gettingstarted/basictutorial.html</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"jprofiler\">JProfiler<a title=\"#jprofiler\" href=\"#jprofiler\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/6438c32f0d2dde577769984a.png\" alt=\"Java VisualVM\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>官网: <a href=\"https://www.ej-technologies.com/products/jprofiler/overview.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ej-technologies.com/products/jprofiler/overview.html</a></p>\n<p>绿色版下载: <a href=\"https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/Mic6vrDkQ1F\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/Mic6vrDkQ1F</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"JVM 命令集","link":"jvm-commands"},"next":{"title":"IntelliJ IDEA 配置","link":"IntelliJ-IDEA-Config"},"plink":"http://l-zm.com/jvm-tools/","toc":[{"id":"jvisualvm(java-visualvm)","title":"jvisualvm(Java VisualVM)","index":"1"},{"id":"memory-analyzer-(eclipse-mat)","title":"Memory Analyzer (Eclipse MAT)","index":"2"},{"id":"jprofiler","title":"JProfiler","index":"3"}],"reading_time":"260 字约 2 分钟"}